VaMBridgeCamera and VaMBridgePerson (Virt-a-Mate Bridge Plugins)
Copyright (c) 2025 MaryJaneVaM

These projects include original code authored by MaryJane and are licensed under
the Creative Commons Attribution‑NonCommercial‑ShareAlike 4.0 International License
(CC BY‑NC‑SA 4.0).

Both plugins provide lightweight TCP communication utilities and JSON-based
protocol handling for external control of Virt‑a‑Mate WindowCamera and Person
atoms.

Third‑party components used in these projects include:

- UnityEngine (Unity 2018 runtime components)
- Virt‑a‑Mate core assemblies (Assembly‑CSharp, plugin interfaces)
- SimpleJSON (lightweight JSON parsing library)
- .NET / Mono standard library components (System, System.Net.Sockets, etc.)

These components are licensed under their respective open‑source or proprietary
licenses. No modifications have been made to these third‑party libraries, and
their licenses and copyright notices remain the property of their
respective authors.

This NOTICE file is provided for attribution and licensing transparency.
